    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>👑👑 LONG LIVE THE SHARK KING!!👑👑</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>We will be releasing the full game very soon, but until then grab the demo version and play against Meta Quest VR players now.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;The Shark King&quot; is coming to SHARKS! Look out for him next time you're playing, he loves giving out Royal Tokens to unlock free cosmetics and goldfish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ You're a shark</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Hang out with friends</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Proximity voice chat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Public and Private lobbies/rooms</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ 100's of cosmetics to express your true shark </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦈 <strong>You're a shark</strong>: use your mouth to bite, grab, carry, place, build and attack in this multiplayer physics sandbox game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/786a336a60ee79b08004f23530670c9e.poster.avif?t=1756115943\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/786a336a60ee79b08004f23530670c9e.webm?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/786a336a60ee79b08004f23530670c9e.mp4?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦈 <strong>Swim around</strong> to collect hidden treasures and send them up to the FIN-TASTIC SALVAGE COMPANY for a reward: will you work together, or make it every shark for themselves?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/0000aeecf027b87ac456ec5922c51d01.poster.avif?t=1756115943\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/0000aeecf027b87ac456ec5922c51d01.webm?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/0000aeecf027b87ac456ec5922c51d01.mp4?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦈 <strong>Unique third-person VR locomotion system</strong> that only needs your head and one controller, plus you can play sitting, standing or room-scale.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/34fdc90bb1b8df7c7672ebd0fbd40d9c.poster.avif?t=1756115943\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/34fdc90bb1b8df7c7672ebd0fbd40d9c.webm?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/34fdc90bb1b8df7c7672ebd0fbd40d9c.mp4?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦈 <strong>Do everything with your mouth</strong> (you're a shark so you don't have hands): grab, carry, fling, place, build, open, activate, attack and (of course) eat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/0ccb978ae4f916627c801aa970f90417.poster.avif?t=1756115943\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/0ccb978ae4f916627c801aa970f90417.webm?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/0ccb978ae4f916627c801aa970f90417.mp4?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦈 <strong>Play with your non-VR friends</strong> on the flat-screen version. Each game is a quick snack-sized round so it's perfect to just drop-in or -out whenever you've got a spare minute.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/a03aeb8bb9eb0740a98f4a084469f3bb.poster.avif?t=1756115943\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/a03aeb8bb9eb0740a98f4a084469f3bb.webm?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/a03aeb8bb9eb0740a98f4a084469f3bb.mp4?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦈 <strong>Visit the Shark Shop</strong>, with a rotating inventory of items to unlock and wear to express your true shark.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/87519d4f636f729d9bf4109e7092110c.poster.avif?t=1756115943\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/87519d4f636f729d9bf4109e7092110c.webm?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2315970/extras/87519d4f636f729d9bf4109e7092110c.mp4?t=1756115943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🦈 <strong>Sharks is Early Access</strong> which means we are constantly adding new updates based on your feedback. Visit our  Discord to connect with other players, influence the design of the final game and collect free in-game perks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>** DOWNLOAD THE DEMO NOW FOR FREE NOW!! **</strong></p>",
